Twas the night before Christmas, when all through the house
Not a creature was stirring, not dare would a mouse;
Our stockings were hung by the chimney with care,
In hopes that St. Francis soon would be there;
Pips and I were nestled all snug with our treats;
While visions of bully sticks took form in our feet;
With 🇺🇸 🇬🇧 dads debating the tune to Away in a Manger;
Umm who cares anyway? It’s hardly a game-changer… 😂 #nightbeforechristmas
